snippet.title: The GG Shinobi: Stage 1 - Highway
snippet.description: This game means a lot to me. It was the first game for the Game Gear that I ever bought (even though I didn't own one at the time -- it was my sister's) and despite how difficult it was (This is only the second time I have ever managed to complete it) I was incredibly happy with it.
